Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還用問嗎？想聽心愛的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}開玩笑的 收到聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}聽好 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}蠢斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}內容很簡單 聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絕對別和比布利歐家族會扯上關系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}家族會？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不然的話 就把那件事告訴你的王子殿下
Comment: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}OP
